{"tid":1792711,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一年前寫嘅《金屋藏貓》係新手機小說平台tbc...連載中","createTime":"2019-12-21T23:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T03:40:48.000Z","uid":218219,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55bf12a82014cfd6fff920dcc3233dd35aab7999","tid":1792711,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T23:56:25.000Z","msg":"大家好，唔知各位巴打絲打仲記唔記得我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年前我係連登講故台寫咗個長篇故事《金屋藏貓》<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/980395/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/980395/page/1</a></span><br />\n最近收到新平台「tbc...」係instagram direct邀請我去寫故<br />\n不過因為暫時我手頭上未有新長篇故事<br />\n所以我修改咗部份內容同錯字，將呢個舊作《金屋藏貓》上載咗係呢個新平台度：<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://tbcstory.com/storyDetail.html?uuid=326b40c9-3a6b-4246-b57f-eef292ae8997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftbcstory.com%2FstoryDetail.html%3Fuuid%3D326b40c9-3a6b-4246-b57f-eef292ae8997&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=9dfe6859\" target=\"_blank\">https://tbcstory.com/storyDetail.html?uuid=326b40c9-3a6b-4246-b57f-eef292ae8997</a></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxpMAoW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxpMAoW.jpg&h=abbcb468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（感謝巴打　藍幫手設計封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n「tbc...」係一個免費小說手機App <br />\n界面大概係咁樣嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOZwMwy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOZwMwy.jpg&h=3bf411ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而我係網上面搵到嘅簡介如下：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">//「tbc&hellip;」，是to be continued的縮寫，中文有「起承轉合」的意思。每個故事都有自己的生命，可以影響別人，讓人思考與啟發。由填詞人林若寧與前商台創作總監Mike Yuen開發的手機應用程式，為文字創作者推出的文字閱讀平台，配以影像與聲效，還有較為互動的文字顯示方式，讓大眾多一個閱讀平台。手機App內現時有19本讀物正式上架，當中包括夕爺的《似是故人來》...... //</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/803704/lifestyle/tbc-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9Fapp-%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F803704%2Flifestyle%2Ftbc-%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259Fapp-%25E9%2596%25B1%25E8%25AE%2580%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=38187e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/803704/lifestyle/tbc-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9Fapp-%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣重溫個故事可以去呢個網度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申翻先：佢哋一蚊都冇畀我，亦不設稿費<br />\n不過聯絡我嘅Staff好有熱誠同耐性，同埋個App幾好用，所以我特意係度推介畀大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hina17G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHina17G.jpg&h=1038f4ae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而第時如果我寫新故事，都<strong>一定</strong>會擺係連登上載<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次多謝咁多位巴絲嘅支持<br />\n呢一年來間中都會收到你哋Direct鼓勵我<br />\n雖然認識我嘅人並唔多，但我都會繼續努力寫故同埋戰勝抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有咩意見都歡迎你哋聯絡我 特別係冇連登acc嘅巴絲<br />\n個人Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/siujeguk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsiujeguk%2F&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=af81a125\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/siujeguk/</a>"},{"pid":"f7247f73120785f96d34dd96165e989623371e7f","tid":1792711,"uid":157481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:17:49.000Z","msg":"有喺tbc追開故，都差唔多兩年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以多個平台睇到樓主嘅故，支持"},{"pid":"0d1c2d854bdf3dc58cfaf4526c706dff6889d2bf","tid":1792711,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7247f73120785f96d34dd96165e989623371e7f","tid":1792711,"uid":157481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:17:49.000Z","msg":"有喺tbc追開故，都差唔多兩年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以多個平台睇到樓主嘅故，支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T00:29:09.000Z","msg":"改格式改到好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過啲對話框設計幾得意"},{"pid":"aa64839ff673357161a9bd702ce147a1131e8315","tid":1792711,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f3a8e410ad6449ad5a0f3455822523aa75ce91","tid":1792711,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T22:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f5da5087c0144c26bc6319ca365a681f9ac151","tid":1792711,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}